  "description": "Howdy folks! I hope everyone’s been having a decent week so far. I’ve been getting really anxious after the sun goes down myself: where I live gets targeted by fascists because of the free market, and the election is getting closer.\nSpeaking of the election, how about Bolivia, right? Imagine having the ability to vote against US imperialism! Sure isn’t what folk’ll be doing in a few Tuesdays here State-side, huh?\n",
